üìå Summary of What We Discussed & Decided
Feature	Decision / Implementation
Pokemon Type Comparison	Show effectiveness as x2, x0.5, etc., and explain calculations clearly to users.
Team Creation	Allow multiple teams (not just one).
Where to Store Teams?	Use Zustand (not useState) for better state management.
"Add to Team" Button	Each Pokemon card in the grid has its own Add to Team button.
Drag & Drop Functionality	Users can drag Pokemon between teams, not inside the same team.
Limit on Teams?	No strict limit, but UI should handle multiple teams (e.g., scrollable list).
Team UI	Each team appears as a card with Pokemon inside.
Pokemon Details Inside Teams	Show image, name, types, and remove button inside the team.
UI for Multiple Teams	Display teams as cards in a grid/list format.
How Drag & Drop Works?	Drag Pokemon from one team card to another.
Team Deletion?	Each team should have a Delete button.
Team Name Editing?	Allow users to rename their teams.